data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of a serene West Lancaster community! This beautifully maintained property boasts 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 modern bathrooms, ensuring comfort and convenience for your family. Plus a large bonus Sun Room perfect for basking in natural light and enjoying tranquil moments year-round! As you step inside, you'll be captivated by the newer counter tops. The front and backyard have been meticulously landscaped, featuring lush greenery, a cozy fire pit for gatherings with friends and family, and a charming Koi pond that adds a touch of serenity to your outdoor oasis. With its ideal location, this home offers easy access to the freeway and a nearby shopping center, making daily errands a breeze. This move-in-ready gem is waiting for you to call it home, so don't miss out on the opportunity to make it yours today!
